data.description: Welcome to 2105 Crawford Road, a delightful one-story updated ranch residence nestled in the heart of Raleigh, North Carolina. This charming home offers a perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and style, making it an ideal choice for those seeking a cozy retreat in a vibrant community close to downtown, schools, parks, and shopping centers. This 3 bedroom ranch has updated LVP flooring, fresh paint, and is move in ready for it’s new owner!  This cozy, open-concept design welcomes you into a bright and airy living space with an electric fireplace, and the kitchen is updated with modern appliances and plenty of counter space.  Property includes a back patio with gazebo, extra storage shed and room to create a private entertainment space.  All for less than $300K this close to downtown Raleigh!  No HOA so a great opportunity for a rentals also!
